---
import Container from "../common/Container.astro";
---

<section class="section">
  <Container>

    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Why Sulav Yatra Exists</h2>

      <p class="intro">
        Traveling Nepal shouldn't require spending hours searching through
        scattered blogs, outdated forums, and unreliable information.
      </p>

      <p>
        Sulav Yatra exists to make Nepal easier to explore through trusted
        travel guides, local insights, cultural stories, and practical travel
        information. Whether you're planning your first trip or looking to
        discover hidden gems, our goal is to help you explore Nepal with
        confidence.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillars">

      <article class="pillar-card">
        <h3>Trusted Information</h3>
        <p>
          Reliable travel guides, destination insights, and practical
          information designed to help travelers make informed decisions.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="pillar-card">
        <h3>Local Knowledge</h3>
        <p>
          Discover Nepal through local stories, firsthand experiences,
          cultural insights, and community-driven recommendations.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="pillar-card">
        <h3>Growing Travel Network</h3>
        <p>
          Bringing together travelers, contributors, and travel partners
          to build a stronger tourism ecosystem for Nepal.
        </p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="action">
      <a href="why-sulav-yatra-exists" class="button">
        Learn More
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</section>

<style>
  .section-header {
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .section-header p:last-child {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .pillar-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pillar-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .action {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>